WEBVTT

00:08:27.984 --> 00:08:30.014
heading for the gate, we pause.

00:08:30.038 --> 00:08:32.223
Anyone who wants --

00:08:32.247 --> 00:08:34.971
fellow residents, family,
nurses, volunteers,

00:08:34.995 --> 00:08:37.439
the hearse drivers too, now --

00:08:37.463 --> 00:08:41.890
shares a story or a song or silence,

00:08:41.914 --> 00:08:44.702
as we sprinkle the body
with flower petals.

00:08:45.282 --> 00:08:47.586
It takes a few minutes;

00:08:47.610 --> 00:08:52.975
it's a sweet, simple parting image
to usher in grief with warmth,

00:08:52.999 --> 00:08:54.710
rather than repugnance.

00:08:56.060 --> 00:09:01.106
Contrast that with the typical experience
in the hospital setting,